original_client_text.markup_text:
Jane always gravitated toward music that spoke to her heart. “You get what you give” by the New Radicals was her artist anthem of all anthems. This song held such a special place in Jane’s heart that this was the song she was going to sing on @America’s Got Talent if they wouldn’t let her sing an original.
•
Nightbirde’s version of “You Get What You Give” is being released on 2/19/24 - the 2 year anniversary of her passing.
•
You can preorder the song by clicking the link in the bio. This song feels like it was written by Jane herself.
•
#nightbirde #nightbird #yougetwhatyougive #newRadicals #cover #itsOk #agt #encourage #hope #nightbirdeLegacy
